# File Deletion Restriction

**All file delete operations are restricted to paths under `/Users/rock.xu/github/` only.**

## Rules

- ONLY delete files whose absolute path starts with `/Users/rock.xu/github/`
- NEVER delete any file outside of `/Users/rock.xu/github/`, even if the user requests it
- If a delete is requested for a path outside `/Users/rock.xu/github/`, refuse and explain the restriction
- This applies to all delete methods: the Delete tool, `rm`, `rm -rf`, `trash`, `unlink`, or any other file removal command

## Before Any Delete

1. Resolve the full absolute path of the target file/directory
2. Verify the path starts with `/Users/rock.xu/github/`
3. If it does NOT, refuse the deletion and inform the user
